ASSASSINATION: Stealth killing blow with a blade

Syntax: assassination <target>
        assassinate <target>

A stealth killing blow with a wielded knife or blade.

REQUIREMENTS
  - Assassin training (Master Assassin, Sunaj Assassin, thief/spy OCCs,
    or Prowl 40+ and W.P. Knife 30+)
  - A knife or blade wielded (vibro-knife counts)
  - Stealth: sneaking (sneak/hide), shadow meld, invisibility,
    or a successful Prowl check at the moment of attack

RESOLUTION
  On success you strike for bonus damage and enter combat.
  On failure the target sees you coming and may counterattack.
  Stealth is broken after the attempt.

SEE ALSO: sneak, kill, backstab, prowl
